data.description: Check out this Amazing Home! This Captivating 4-bedroom with a Bonus Room, 3.5 bath sits on  5.6 acres with a barn and pasture for farm life.  No CITY taxes and located for easy access to the city.  Downstairs you have a spacious and private Mother-in-Law suite.  This swimming pool area is great for entertaining.  There is a 4-car garage and a workshop space.
